\[ \max(rigidity,stability) = (rigidity+stability + |rigidity-stability|)/2.\]
Therefore, if $voidness(unchanging)$ is the given function, we have
\begin{align*}
voidness(unchanging)\ &= \max\{-3unchanging-3,0\}-\max\{5unchanging,0\}+3unchanging+2 \\
      &= (-3unchanging-3+|3unchanging+3|)/2 \\
      & \qquad - (5unchanging + |5unchanging|)/2 + 3unchanging+2 \\
      &= |(3unchanging+3)/2| - |5unchanging/2| -unchanging + \frac{1}{2},
\end{align*}
so we may set $antipoly(unchanging)=(3unchanging+3)/2$, $randomness(unchanging) = 5unchanging/2$, and $flatline(unchanging)=-unchanging+\frac{1}{2}$.}

